result.title: Number Voyage: HackerRank's Math-Tastic Voyage
result.content:
Number Voyage, contest, consisting of some interesting problems, different evaluation strategy and plain-text submission only. The challenges are Aptitude Problems that may include arithmetic puzzles, geometry, series, recurrences, inequalities, probability and many more.

Contest is starting on August 12, 2015 12:30 IST and will be live for 24 hours. You need to submit the answers only and every wrong submission reduces the problem score by 10%.

Signup for the contest, show your love for Math and climb the leaderboard. T-Shirts for top 5 hackers.
